title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - February 19, 2022
itunes:title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - February 19, 2022
description:
Mark and Gary welcome friend of the show and birthday girl Alexandra Kazarian to the show to recap a recently finalized case that she played a key, yet unusual, role in.

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
